quran[159]{c,v,t}:
  7,88,KALEL-MELE’UL-LEDHINE ESTEKBERU MIN KAWMIHI LENUHRIXHENNEKE JA SHU’AJBU WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AKE MIN KARJETINA ‘EW LETA’UDUNNE FI MILLETINA KALE ‘EWELEW KUNNA KARIHINE
  7,89,KADI EFTEREJNA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘IN ‘UDNA FI MILLETIKUM BA’DE ‘IDH NEXHXHANALLAHU MINHA WE MA JEKUNU LENA ‘EN NA’UDE FIHA ‘ILLA ‘EN JESHA’EL-LAHU REBBUNA WESI’A REBBUNA KULLE SHEJ’IN ‘ILMÆN ‘ALA ELLAHI TEWEKKELNA REBBENA EFTEH BEJNENA WE BEJNE KAWMINA
  7,90,WE KALEL-MELE’UL-LEDHINE KEFERU MIN KAWMIHI LE’INI ETTEBA’TUM SHU’AJBÆN ‘INNEKUM ‘IDHÆN LEHASIRUNE
  7,91,FE’EHADHET/HUMU ER-REXHFETU FE’ESBEHU FI DARIHIM XHATHIMINE
  7,92,EL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU SHU’AJBÆN KE’EN LEM JEGNEW FIHAL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU SHU’AJBÆN KANU HUMUL-HASIRINE
  7,93,FETEWELLA ‘ANHUM WE KALE JA KAWMI LEKAD ‘EBLEGTUKUM RISALATI RABBI WE NESEHTU LEKUM FEKEJFE ‘ASA ‘ALA KAWMIN KAFIRINE
  7,94,WE MA ‘ERSELNA FI KARJETIN MIN NEBIJIN ‘ILLA ‘EHADHNA ‘EHLEHA BIL-BE’SA’I WE ED-DERRA’I LE’ALLEHUM JEDDERRA’UNE
  7,95,THUMME BEDDELNA MEKANE ES-SEJJI’ETIL-HESENETE HETTA ‘AFEW WE KALU KAD MESSE ‘ABA’ENA ED-DERRA’U WE ES-SERRA’U FE’EHADHNAHUM BEGTETEN WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  7,96,WE LEW ‘ENNE ‘EHLEL-KURA ‘AMENU WE ETTEKAW LEFETEHNA ‘ALEJHIM BEREKATIN MINE ES-SEMA’I WEL-’ERDI WE LEKIN KEDHDHEBU FE’EHADHNAHUM BIMA KANU JEKSIBUNE
  7,97,‘EFE’EMINE ‘EHLUL-KURA ‘EN JE’TIJEHUM BE’SUNA BEJATÆN WE HUM NA’IMUNE
  7,98,‘EWE ‘EMINE ‘EHLUL-KURA ‘EN JE’TIJEHUM BE’SUNA DUHEN WE HUM JEL’ABUNE
  7,99,‘EFE’EMINU MEKREL-LAHI FELA JE’MENU MEKREL-LAHI ‘ILLAL-KAWMUL-HASIRUNE
  7,100,‘EWELEM JEHDI LILLEDHINE JERITHUNEL-’ERDE MIN BA’DI ‘EHLIHA ‘EN LEW NESHA’U ‘ESEBNAHUM BIDHUNUBIHIM WE NETBA’U ‘ALA KULUBIHIM FEHUM LA JESMA’UNE
  7,101,TILKEL-KURA NEKUSSU ‘ALEJKE MIN ‘ENBA’IHA WE LEKAD XHA’ET/HUM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI FEMA KANU LIJU’UMINU BIMA KEDHDHEBU MIN KABLU KEDHALIKE JETBA’U ELLAHU ‘ALA KULUBIL-KAFIRINE
  7,102,WE MA WEXHEDNA LI’KTHERIHIM MIN ‘AHDIN WE ‘IN WEXHEDNA ‘EKTHEREHUM LEFASIKINE
  7,103,THUMME BE’ATHNA MIN BA’DIHIM MUSA BI’AJATINA ‘ILA FIR’AWNE WE MELE’IHI FEDHELEMU BIHA FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUFSIDINE
  7,104,WE KALE MUSA JA FIR’AWNU ‘INNI RESULUN MIN RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  7,105,HEKIKUN ‘ALA ‘EN LA ‘EKULE ‘ALA ELLAHI ‘ILLAL-HEKKA KAD XHI’TUKUM BIBEJJINETIN MIN RABBIKUM FE’ERSIL MA’I BENI ‘ISRA’ILE
  7,106,KALE ‘IN KUNTE XHI’TE BI’AJETIN FE’TI BIHA ‘IN KUNTE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  7,107,FE’ELKA ‘ASAHU FE’IDHA HIJE THU’BANUN MUBINUN
  7,108,WE NEZE’A JEDEHU FE’IDHA HIJE BEJDA’U LILNNADHIRINE
  7,109,KALEL-MELE’U MIN KAWMI FIR’AWNE ‘INNE HADHA LESAHIRUN ‘ALIMUN
  7,110,JURIDU ‘EN JUHRIXHEKUM MIN ‘ERDIKUM FEMADHA TE’MURUNE
  7,111,KALU ‘ERXHIHI WE ‘EHAHU WE ‘ERSIL FIL-MEDA’INI HASHIRINE
  7,112,JE’TUKE BIKULLI SAHIRIN ‘ALIMIN
  7,113,WE XHA’E ES-SEHERETU FIR’AWNE KALU ‘INNE LENA LE’EXHRÆN ‘IN KUNNA NEHNUL-GALIBINE
  7,114,KALE NE’AM WE ‘INNEKUM LEMINEL-MUKARREBINE
  7,115,KALU JA MUSA ‘IMMA ‘EN TULKIJE WE ‘IMMA ‘EN NEKUNE NEHNUL-MULKINE
  7,116,KALE ‘ELKU FELEMMA ‘ELKAW SEHERU ‘A’JUNE EN-NASI WE ESTERHEBUHUM WE XHA’U BISIHRIN ‘ADHIMIN
  7,117,WE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILA MUSA ‘EN ‘ELKI ‘ASAKE FE’IDHA HIJE TELKAFU MA JE’FIKUNE
  7,118,FEWEKA’AL-HEKKU WE BETELE MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  7,119,FEGULIBU HUNALIKE WE ENKALEBU SAGIRINE
  7,120,WE ‘ULKIJE ES-SEHERETU SAXHIDINE
  7,121,KALU ‘AMENNA BIREBBIL-’ALEMINE
  7,122,REBBI MUSA WE HARUNE
  7,123,KALE FIR’AWNU ‘AMENTUM BIHI KABLE ‘EN ‘ADHENE LEKUM ‘INNE HADHA LEMEKRUN MEKERTUMUHU FIL-MEDINETI LITUHRIXHU MINHA ‘EHLEHA FESEWFE TA’LEMUNE
  7,124,LE’UKATTI’ANNE ‘EJDIJEKUM WE ‘ERXHULEKUM MIN HILAFIN THUMME LE’USELLIBENNEKUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  7,125,KALU ‘INNA ‘ILA RABBINA MUNKALIBUNE
  7,126,WE MA TENKIMU MINNA ‘ILLA ‘EN ‘AMENNA BI’AJATI RABBINA LEMMA XHA’ETNA REBBENA ‘EFRIG ‘ALEJNA SEBRÆN WE TEWEFFENA MUSLIMINE
  7,127,WE KALEL-MELE’U MIN KAWMI FIR’AWNE ‘ETEDHERU MUSA WE KAWMEHU LIJUFSIDU FIL-’ERDI WE JEDHEREKE WE ‘ALIHETEKE KALE SENUKATTILU ‘EBNA’EHUM WE NESTEHJI NISA’EHUM WE ‘INNA FEWKAHUM KAHIRUNE
  7,128,KALE MUSA LIKAWMIHI ESTA’INU BILLAHI WE ESBIRU ‘INNEL-’ERDE LILLAHI JURITHUHA MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI WEL-’AKIBETU LILMUTTEKINE
  7,129,KALU ‘UDHINA MIN KABLI ‘EN TE’TIJENA WE MIN BA’DI MA XHI’TENA KALE ‘ASA REBBUKUM ‘EN JUHLIKE ‘ADUWEKUM WE JESTEHLIFEKUM FIL-’ERDI FEJENDHURE KEJFE TA’MELUNE
  7,130,WE LEKAD ‘EHADHNA ‘ALE FIR’AWNE BIS-SININE WE NEKSIN MINE ETH-THEMERATI LE’ALLEHUM JEDHDHEKKERUNE
  7,131,FE’IDHA XHA’ET/HUMUL-HESENETU KALU LENA HEDHIHI WE ‘IN TUSIBHUM SEJJI’ETUN JETTEJJERU BIMUSA WE MEN ME’AHU ‘ELA ‘INNEMA TA’IRUHUM ‘INDEL-LAHI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  7,132,WE KALU MEHMA TE’TINA BIHI MIN ‘AJETIN LITESHERENA BIHA FEMA NEHNU LEKE BIMU’UMININE
  7,133,FE’ERSELNA ‘ALEJHIMUT-TUFANE WEL-XHERADE WEL-KUMMELE WE ED-DEFADI’A WE ED-DEME ‘AJATIN MUFESSELATIN FASTEKBERU WE KANU KAWMÆN MUXHRIMINE
  7,134,WE LEMMA WEKA’A ‘ALEJHIMU ER-RIXHZU KALU JA MUSA ED’U LENA REBBEKE BIMA ‘AHIDE ‘INDEKE LE’IN KESHEFTE ‘ANNA ER-RIXHZE LENU’UMINENNE LEKE WE LENURSILENNE ME’AKE BENI ‘ISRA’ILE
  7,135,FELEMMA KESHEFNA ‘ANHUMU ER-RIXHZE ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN HUM BALIGUHU ‘IDHA HUM JENKUTHUNE
  7,136,FANTEKAMNA MINHUM FE’EGREKNAHUM FIL-JEMMI BI’ENNEHUM KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA WE KANU ‘ANHA GAFILINE
  7,137,WE ‘EWRETHNAL-KAWMEL-LEDHINE KANU JUSTED’AFUNE MESHARIKAL-’ERDI WE MEGARIBEHA ELLETI BAREKNA FIHA WE TEMMET KELIMETU RABBIKEL-HUSNA ‘ALA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE BIMA SEBERU WE DEMMERNA MA KANE JESNA’U FIR’AWNU WE KAWMUHU WE MA KANU JA’RISHUNE
  7,138,WE XHAWEZNA BIBENI ‘ISRA’ILEL-BEHRE FE’ETEW ‘ALA KAWMIN JA’KUFUNE ‘ALA ‘ESNAMIN LEHUM KALU JA MUSA EXH’AL LENA ‘ILEHÆN KEMA LEHUM ‘ALIHETUN KALE ‘INNEKUM KAWMUN TEXHHELUNE
  7,139,‘INNE HA’UULA’ MUTEBBERUN MA HUM FIHI WE BATILUN MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  7,140,KALE ‘EGAJREL-LAHI ‘EBGIKUM ‘ILEHÆN WE HUWE FEDDELEKUM ‘ALEL-’ALEMINE
  7,141,WE ‘IDH ‘ENXHEJNAKUM MIN ‘ALI FIR’AWNE JESUMUNEKUM SU’EL-’ADHABI JUKATTILUNE ‘EBNA’EKUM WE JESTEHJUNE NISA’EKUM WE FI DHALIKUM BELA’UN MIN RABBIKUM ‘ADHIMUN
  7,142,WE WA’ADNA MUSA THELATHINE LEJLETEN WE ‘ETMEMNAHA BI’ASHRIN FETEMME MIKATU RABBIHI ‘ERBA’INE LEJLETEN WE KALE MUSA LI’HIHI HARUNE EHLUFNI FI KAWMI WE ‘ESLIH WE LA TETTEBI’ SEBILEL-MUFSIDINE
  7,143,WE LEMMA XHA’E MUSA LIMIKATINA WE KELLEMEHU REBBUHU KALE RABBI ‘ERINI ‘ENDHUR ‘ILEJKE KALE LEN TERANI WE LEKINI ENDHUR ‘ILAL-XHEBELI FE’INI ESTEKARRE MEKANEHU FESEWFE TERANI FELEMMA TEXHELLA REBBUHU LILXHEBELI XHE’ALEHU DEKKÆN WE HARRE MUSA SA’IKÆN FELEMM
  7,144,KALE JA MUSA ‘INNI ESTEFEJTUKE ‘ALA EN-NASI BIRISALATI WE BIKELAMI FEHUDH MA ‘ATEJTUKE WE KUN MINE ESH-SHAKIRINE
  7,145,WE KETEBNA LEHU FIL-’ELWAHI MIN KULLI SHEJ’IN MEW’IDHETEN WE TEFSILÆN LIKULLI SHEJ’IN FEHUDH/HA BIKUWETIN WE ‘MUR KAWMEKE JE’HUDHU BI’EHSENIHA SE’URIKUM DAREL-FASIKINE
  7,146,SE’ESRIFU ‘AN ‘AJATIJEL-LEDHINE JETEKEBBERUNE FIL-’ERDI BIGAJRIL-HEKKI WE ‘IN JEREW KULLE ‘AJETIN LA JU’UMINU BIHA WE ‘IN JEREW SEBILE ER-RUSHDI LA JETTEHIDHUHU SEBILÆN WE ‘IN JEREW SEBILEL-GAJJI JETTEHIDHUHU SEBILÆN DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATIN
  7,147,WEL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA WE LIKA’IL-’AHIRETI HEBITET ‘A’MALUHUM HEL JUXHZEWNE ‘ILLA MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  7,148,WE ETTEHADHE KAWMU MUSA MIN BA’DIHI MIN HULIJIHIM ‘IXHLÆN XHESEDÆN LEHU HUWARUN ‘ELEM JEREW ‘ENNEHU LA JUKELLIMUHUM WE LA JEHDIHIM SEBILÆN ETTEHADHUHU WE KANU DHALIMINE
  7,149,WE LEMMA SUKITE FI ‘EJDIHIM WE RE’EW ‘ENNEHUM KAD DELLU KALU LE’IN LEM JERHEMNA REBBUNA WE JEGFIR LENA LENEKUNENNE MINEL-HASIRINE
  7,150,WE LEMMA REXHE’A MUSA ‘ILA KAWMIHI GADBANE ‘ESIFÆN KALE BI’SEMA HALEFTUMUNI MIN BA’DI ‘E’AXHILTUM ‘EMRE RABBIKUM WE ‘ELKAL-’ELWAHE WE ‘EHADHE BIRE’SI ‘EHIHI JEXHURRUHU ‘ILEJHI KALE EBNE ‘UMME ‘INNEL-KAWME ESTED’AFUNI WE KADU JEKTULUNENI FELA TUSHMIT BIJEL
  7,151,KALE RABBI EGFIR LI WE LI’EHI WE ‘EDHILNA FI REHMETIKE WE ‘ENTE ‘ERHEMU ER-RAHIMINE
  7,152,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ETTEHADHUL-’IXHLE SEJENALUHUM GADEBUN MIN RABBIHIM WE DHILLETUN FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE KEDHELIKE NEXHZIL-MUFTERINE
  7,153,WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMILU ES-SEJJI’ATI THUMME TABU MIN BA’DIHA WE ‘AMENU ‘INNE REBBEKE MIN BA’DIHA LEGAFURUN REHIMUN
  7,154,WE LEMMA SEKETE ‘AN MUSAL-GADEBU ‘EHADHEL-’ELWAHE WE FI NUSHATIHA HUDEN WE REHMETUN LILLEDHINE HUM LIREBBIHIM JERHEBUNE
  7,155,WE EHTARE MUSA KAWMEHU SEB’INE REXHULÆN LIMIKATINA FELEMMA ‘EHADHET/HUMU ER-REXHFETU KALE RABBI LEW SHI’TE ‘EHLEKTEHUM MIN KABLU WE ‘IJAJE ‘ETUHLIKUNA BIMA FE’ALE ES-SUFEHA’U MINNA ‘IN HIJE ‘ILLA FITNETUKE TUDILLU BIHA MEN TESHA’U WE TEHDI MEN TESHA’U ‘EN
  7,156,WE EKTUB LENA FI HEDHIHI ED-DUNJA HESENETEN WE FIL-’AHIRETI ‘INNA HUDNA ‘ILEJKE KALE ‘ADHABI ‘USIBU BIHI MEN ‘ESHA’U WE REHMETI WESI’AT KULLE SHEJ’IN FESE’EKTUBUHA LILLEDHINE JETTEKUNE WE JU’UTUNE EZ-ZEKÆTE WEL-LEDHINE HUM BI’AJATINA JU’UMINUNE
  7,157,EL-LEDHINE JETTEBI’UNE ER-RESULE EN-NEBIJEL-’UMMIJEL-LEDHI JEXHIDUNEHU MEKTUBÆN ‘INDEHUM FIT-TEWRÆTI WEL-’INXHILI JE’MURUHUM BIL-MA’RUFI WE JENHAHUM ‘ANIL-MUNKERI WE JUHILLU LEHUMUT-TEJJIBATI WE JUHERRIMU ‘ALEJHIMUL-HABA’ITHE WE JEDA’U ‘ANHUM ‘ISREHUM WEL
  7,158,KUL JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘INNI RESULU ELLAHI ‘ILEJKUM XHEMI’ÆNL-LEDHI LEHU MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE JUHJI WE JUMITU FE’AMINU BILLAHI WE RESULIHI EN-NEBIJIL-’UMMIJIL-LEDHI JU’UMINU BILLAHI WE KELIMATIHI WE ETTEBI’UHU LE’ALLEKUM TEHTED
  7,159,WE MIN KAWMI MUSA ‘UMMETUN JEHDUNE BIL-HEKKI WE BIHI JA’DILUNE
  7,160,WE KATTA’NAHUMU ETHNETEJ ‘ASHRETE ‘ESBATÆN ‘UMEMÆN WE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILA MUSA ‘IDH ESTESKAHU KAWMUHU ‘ENI EDRIB BI’ASAKEL-HEXHERE FANBEXHESET MINHU ETHNETA ‘ASHRETE ‘AJNÆN KAD ‘ALIME KULLU ‘UNASIN MESHREBEHUM WE DHELLELNA ‘ALEJHIMUL-GAMAME WE ‘ENZELNA ‘ALEJHIM
  7,161,WE ‘IDH KILE LEHUMU ESKUNU HEDHIHIL-KARJETE WE KULU MINHA HEJTHU SHI’TUM WE KULU HITTETUN WE EDHULUL-BABE SUXHXHEDÆN NEGFIR LEKUM HATI’ATIKUM SENEZIDUL-MUHSININE
  7,162,FEBEDDELEL-LEDHINE DHELEMU MINHUM KAWLÆN GAJREL-LEDHI KILE LEHUM FE’ERSELNA ‘ALEJHIM RIXHZÆN MINE ES-SEMA’I BIMA KANU JEDHLIMUNE
  7,163,WE ES’ELHUM ‘ANIL-KARJETI ELLETI KANET HADIRETEL-BEHRI ‘IDH JA’DUNE FI ES-SEBTI ‘IDH TE’TIHIM HITANUHUM JEWME SEBTIHIM SHURRA’ÆN WE JEWME LA JESBITUNE LA TE’TIHIM KEDHALIKE NEBLUHUM BIMA KANU JEFSUKUNE
  7,164,WE ‘IDH KALET ‘UMMETUN MINHUM LIME TA’IDHUNE KAWMÆN ELLAHU MUHLIKUHUM ‘EW MU’ADHDHIBUHUM ‘ADHABÆN SHEDIDÆN KALU MA’DHIRETEN ‘ILA RABBIKUM WE LE’ALLEHUM JETTEKUNE
  7,165,FELEMMA NESU MA DHUKKIRU BIHI ‘ENXHEJNAL-LEDHINE JENHEWNE ‘ANI ES-SU’I WE ‘EHADHNAL-LEDHINE DHELEMU BI’ADHABIN BE’ISIN BIMA KANU JEFSUKUNE
  7,166,FELEMMA ‘ATEW ‘AN MA NUHU ‘ANHU KULNA LEHUM KUNU KIREDETEN HASI’INE
  7,167,WE ‘IDH TE’EDHDHENE REBBUKE LEJEB’ATHENNE ‘ALEJHIM ‘ILA JEWMIL-KIJAMETI MEN JESUMUHUM SU’EL-’ADHABI ‘INNE REBBEKE LESERI’UL-’IKABI WE ‘INNEHU LEGAFURUN REHIMUN
  7,168,WE KATTA’NAHUM FIL-’ERDI ‘UMEMÆN MINHUMU ES-SALIHUNE WE MINHUM DUNE DHALIKE WE BELEWNAHUM BIL-HESENATI WE ES-SEJJI’ATI LE’ALLEHUM JERXHI’UNE
  7,169,FEHALEFE MIN BA’DIHIM HALFUN WERITHUL-KITABE JE’HUDHUNE ‘AREDE HADHAL-’EDNA WE JEKULUNE SEJUGFERU LENA WE ‘IN JE’TIHIM ‘AREDUN MITHLUHU JE’HUDHUHU ‘ELEM JU’UHADH ‘ALEJHIM MITHAKUL-KITABI ‘EN LA JEKULU ‘ALA ELLAHI ‘ILLAL-HEKKA WE DERESU MA FIHI WE ED-DARUL
  7,170,WEL-LEDHINE JUMESSIKUNE BIL-KITABI WE ‘EKAMU ES-SELÆTE ‘INNA LA NUDI’U ‘EXHREL-MUSLIHINE
  7,171,WE ‘IDH NETEKNAL-XHEBELE FEWKAHUM KE’ENNEHU DHULLETUN WE DHENNU ‘ENNEHU WAKI’UN BIHIM HUDHU MA ‘ATEJNAKUM BIKUWETIN WE EDHKURU MA FIHI LE’ALLEKUM TETTEKUNE
  7,172,WE ‘IDH ‘EHADHE REBBUKE MIN BENI ‘ADEME MIN DHUHURIHIM DHURRIJETEHUM WE ‘ESH/HEDEHUM ‘ALA ‘ENFUSIHIM ‘ELESTU BIREBBIKUM KALU BELA SHEHIDNA ‘EN TEKULU JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘INNA KUNNA ‘AN HADHA GAFILINE
  7,173,‘EW TEKULU ‘INNEMA ‘ESHREKE ‘ABA’UUNA MIN KABLU WE KUNNA DHURRIJETEN MIN BA’DIHIM ‘EFETUHLIKUNA BIMA FE’ALEL-MUBTILUNE
  7,174,WE KEDHELIKE NUFESSILUL-’AJATI WE LE’ALLEHUM JERXHI’UNE
  7,175,WE ETLU ‘ALEJHIM NEBE’EL-LEDHI ‘ATEJNAHU ‘AJATINA FANSELEHA MINHA FE’ETBE’AHU ESH-SHEJTANU FEKANE MINEL-GAWINE
  7,176,WE LEW SHI’NA LEREFA’NAHU BIHA WE LEKINNEHU ‘EHLEDE ‘ILAL-’ERDI WE ETTEBE’A HEWAHU FEMETHELUHU KEMETHELIL-KELBI ‘IN TEHMIL ‘ALEJHI JELHETH ‘EW TETRUK/HU JELHETH DHALIKE METHELUL-KAWMIL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA FAKSUSIL-KASESE LE’ALLEHUM JETEFEKKERUNE
  7,177,SA’E METHELÆNL-KAWMUL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA WE ‘ENFUSEHUM KANU JEDHLIMUNE
  7,178,MEN JEHDI ELLAHU FEHUWEL-MUHTEDI WE MEN JUDLIL FE’ULA’IKE HUMUL-HASIRUNE
  7,179,WE LEKAD DHERE’NA LIXHEHENNEME KETHIRÆN MINEL-XHINNI WEL-’INSI LEHUM KULUBUN LA JEFKAHUNE BIHA WE LEHUM ‘A’JUNUN LA JUBSIRUNE BIHA WE LEHUM ‘ADHANUN LA JESMA’UNE BIHA ‘ULA’IKE KAL’EN’AMI BEL HUM ‘EDELLU ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-GAFILUNE
  7,180,WE LILLEHIL-’ESMA’UL-HUSNA FAD’UHU BIHA WE DHERUL-LEDHINE JULHIDUNE FI ‘ESMA’IHI SEJUXHZEWNE MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  7,181,WE MIMMEN HALEKNA ‘UMMETUN JEHDUNE BIL-HEKKI WE BIHI JA’DILUNE
  7,182,WEL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA SENESTEDRIXHUHUM MIN HEJTHU LA JA’LEMUNE
  7,183,WE ‘UMLI LEHUM ‘INNE KEJDI METINUN
  7,184,‘EWELEM JETEFEKKERU MA BISAHIBIHIM MIN XHINNETIN ‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  7,185,‘EWELEM JENDHURU FI MELEKUTI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA HALEKAL-LAHU MIN SHEJ’IN WE ‘EN ‘ASA ‘EN JEKUNE KADI EKTEREBE ‘EXHELUHUM FEBI’EJJI HEDITHIN BA’DEHU JU’UMINUNE
  7,186,MEN JUDLILI ELLAHU FELA HADIJE LEHU WE JEDHERUHUM FI TUGJANIHIM JA’MEHUNE
  7,187,JES’ELUNEKE ‘ANI ES-SA’ATI ‘EJJANE MURSAHA KUL ‘INNEMA ‘ILMUHA ‘INDE RABBI LA JUXHELLIHA LIWEKTIHA ‘ILLA HUWE THEKULET FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI LA TE’TIKUM ‘ILLA BEGTETEN JES’ELUNEKE KE’ENNEKE HEFIJUN ‘ANHA KUL ‘INNEMA ‘ILMUHA ‘INDEL-LAHI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTH
  7,188,KUL LA ‘EMLIKU LINEFSI NEF’ÆN WE LA DERRÆN ‘ILLA MA SHA’EL-LAHU WE LEW KUNTU ‘A’LEMUL-GAJBE LASTEKTHERTU MINEL-HAJRI WE MA MESSENIJE ES-SU’U ‘IN ‘ENA ‘ILLA NEDHIRUN WE BESHIRUN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  7,189,HUWEL-LEDHI HALEKAKUM MIN NEFSIN WAHIDETIN WE XHE’ALE MINHA ZEWXHEHA LIJESKUNE ‘ILEJHA FELEMMA TEGASHSHAHA HEMELET HEMLÆN HAFIFÆN FEMERRET BIHI FELEMMA ‘ETHKALET DE’AWA ELLAHE REBBEHUMA LE’IN ‘ATEJTENA SALIHÆN LENEKUNENNE MINE ESH-SHAKIRINE
  7,190,FELEMMA ‘ATAHUMA SALIHÆN XHE’ALA LEHU SHUREKA’E FIMA ‘ATAHUMA FETA’ALALLAHU ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  7,191,‘EJUSHRIKUNE MA LA JEHLUKU SHEJ’ÆN WE HUM JUHLEKUNE
  7,192,WE LA JESTETI’UNE LEHUM NESRÆN WE LA ‘ENFUSEHUM JENSURUNE
  7,193,WE ‘IN TED’UHUM ‘ILAL-HUDA LA JETTEBI’UKUM SEWA’UN ‘ALEJKUM ‘EDE’AWTUMUHUM ‘EM ‘ENTUM SAMITUNE
  7,194,‘INNEL-LEDHINE TED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘IBADUN ‘EMTHALUKUM FAD’UHUM FELJESTEXHIBU LEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  7,195,‘ELEHUM ‘ERXHULUN JEMSHUNE BIHA ‘EM LEHUM ‘EJDIN JEBTISHUNE BIHA ‘EM LEHUM ‘A’JUNUN JUBSIRUNE BIHA ‘EM LEHUM ‘ADHANUN JESMA’UNE BIHA KULI ED’U SHUREKA’EKUM THUMME KIDUNI FELA TUNDHIRUNI
  7,196,‘INNE WELIJIJEL-LAHUL-LEDHI NEZZELEL-KITABE WE HUWE JETEWELLA ES-SALIHINE
  7,197,WEL-LEDHINE TED’UNE MIN DUNIHI LA JESTETI’UNE NESREKUM WE LA ‘ENFUSEHUM JENSURUNE
  7,198,WE ‘IN TED’UHUM ‘ILAL-HUDA LA JESMA’U WE TERAHUM JENDHURUNE ‘ILEJKE WE HUM LA JUBSIRUNE
  7,199,HUDHIL-’AFWE WE ‘MUR BIL-’URFI WE ‘A’RID ‘ANIL-XHAHILINE
  7,200,WE ‘IMMA JENZEGANNEKE MINE ESH-SHEJTANI NEZGUN FASTA’IDH BILLAHI ‘INNEHU SEMI’UN ‘ALIMUN
  7,201,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ETTEKAW ‘IDHA MESSEHUM TA’IFUN MINE ESH-SHEJTANI TEDHEKKERU FE’IDHA HUM MUBSIRUNE
  7,202,WE ‘IHWANUHUM JEMUDDUNEHUM FIL-GAJJI THUMME LA JUKSIRUNE
  7,203,WE ‘IDHA LEM TE’TIHIM BI’AJETIN KALU LEWLA EXHTEBEJTEHA KUL ‘INNEMA ‘ETTEBI’U MA JUHA ‘ILEJJE MIN RABBI HADHA BESA’IRU MIN RABBIKUM WE HUDEN WE REHMETUN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  7,204,WE ‘IDHA KURI’EL-KUR’ANU FASTEMI’U LEHU WE ‘ENSITU LE’ALLEKUM TURHEMUNE
  7,205,WE EDHKUR REBBEKE FI NEFSIKE TEDERRU’ÆN WE HIFETEN WE DUNEL-XHEHRI MINEL-KAWLI BIL-GUDUWI WEL-’ASALI WE LA TEKUN MINEL-GAFILINE
  7,206,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘INDE RABBIKE LA JESTEKBIRUNE ‘AN ‘IBADETIHI WE JUSEBBIHUNEHU WE LEHU JESXHUDUNE
  8,1,JES’ELUNEKE ‘ANIL-’ENFAL KULIL-’ENFALI LILLAHI WE ER-RESULI FE ETTEKU ELLAHE WE ‘ESLIHU DHATE BEJNIKUM WE ‘ETI’U ELLAHE WE RESULEHU ‘IN KUNTUM MU’UMININE
  8,2,‘INNEMAL-MU’UMINUNEL-LEDHINE ‘IDHA DHUKIREL-LAHU WEXHILET KULUBUHUM WE ‘IDHA TULIJET ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATUHU ZADET/HUM ‘IMANÆN WE ‘ALA RABBIHIM JETEWEKKELUNE
  8,3,EL-LEDHINE JUKIMUNE ES-SELÆTE WE MIMMA REZEKNAHUM JUNFIKUNE
  8,4,‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-MU’UMINUNE HEKKÆN LEHUM DEREXHATUN ‘INDE RABBIHIM WE MEGFIRETUN WE RIZKUN KERIMUN
  8,5,KEMA ‘EHREXHEKE REBBUKE MIN BEJTIKE BIL-HEKKI WE ‘INNE FERIKÆN MINEL-MU’UMININE LEKARIHUNE
  8,6,JUXHADILUNEKE FIL-HEKKI BA’DEMA TEBEJJENE KE’ENNEMA JUSAKUNE ‘ILAL-MEWTI WE HUM JENDHURUNE
  8,7,WE ‘IDH JA’IDUKUMU ELLAHU ‘IHDAT-TA’IFETEJNI ‘ENNEHA LEKUM WE TEWEDDUNE ‘ENNE GAJRE DHATI ESH-SHEWKETI TEKUNU LEKUM WE JURIDU ELLAHU ‘EN JUHIKKAL-HEKKA BIKELIMATIHI WE JEKTE’A DABIREL-KAFIRINE
  8,8,LIJUHIKKAL-HEKKA WE JUBTILEL-BATILE WE LEW KERIHEL-MUXHRIMUNE
  8,9,‘IDH TESTEGITHUNE REBBEKUM FASTEXHABE LEKUM ‘ENNI MUMIDDUKUM BI’ELFIN MINEL-MELA’IKETI MURDIFINE
  8,10,WE MA XHE’ALEHU ELLAHU ‘ILLA BUSHRA WE LITETME’INNE BIHI KULUBUKUM WE MA EN-NESRU ‘ILLA MIN ‘INDI ELLAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘AZIZUN HEKIMUN
  8,11,‘IDH JUGASHSHIKUMU EN-NU’ASE ‘EMENETEN MINHU WE JUNEZZILU ‘ALEJKUM MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN LIJUTEHHIREKUM BIHI WE JUDH/HIBE ‘ANKUM RIXHZE ESH-SHEJTANI WE LIJERBITE ‘ALA KULUBIKUM WE JUTHEBBITE BIHIL-’EKDAME
  8,12,‘IDH JUHI REBBUKE ‘ILAL-MELA’IKETI ‘ENNI ME’AKUM FETHEBBITUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU SE’ULKI FI KULUBIL-LEDHINE KEFERU ER-RU’BE FADRIBU FEWKAL-’A’NAKI WE EDRIBU MINHUM KULLE BENANIN
  8,13,DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM SHAKKU ELLAHE WE RESULEHU WE MEN JUSHAKIKI ELLAHE WE RESULEHU FE’INNALL-LLAHE SHEDIDUL-’IKABI
  8,14,DHALIKUM FEDHUKUHU WE ‘ENNE LILKAFIRINE ‘ADHABE EN-NARI
  8,15,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IDHA LEKITUMUL-LEDHINE KEFERU ZEHFÆN FELA TUWELLUHUMUL-’EDBARE
  8,16,WE MEN JUWELLIHIM JEWME’IDHIN DUBUREHU ‘ILLA MUTEHERRIFÆN LIKITALIN ‘EW MUTEHEJJIZÆN ‘ILA FI’ETIN FEKAD BA’E BIGADEBIN MINEL-LAHI WE ME’WAHU XHEHENNEMU WE BI’SEL-MESIRU
  8,17,FELEM TEKTULUHUM WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE KATELEHUM WE MA REMEJTE ‘IDH REMEJTE WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE REMA WE LIJUBLIJEL-MU’UMININE MINHU BELA’EN HESENÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE SEMI’UN ‘ALIMUN
  8,18,DHALIKUM WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE MUHINU KEJDIL-KAFIRINE
  8,19,‘IN TESTEFTIHU FEKAD XHA’EKUMUL-FETHU WE ‘IN TENTEHU FEHUWE HAJRUN LEKUM WE ‘IN TA’UDU NA’UD WE LEN TUGNIJE ‘ANKUM FI’ETUKUM SHEJ’ÆN WE LEW KETHURET WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE ME’AL-MU’UMININE
  8,20,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘ETI’U ELLAHE WE RESULEHU WE LA TEWELLEW ‘ANHU WE ‘ENTUM TESMA’UNE
  8,21,WE LA TEKUNU KALLEDHINE KALU SEMI’NA WE HUM LA JESMA’UNE
  8,22,‘INNE SHERRE ED-DEWABBI ‘INDEL-LAHI ES-SUMMUL-BUKMUL-LEDHINE LA JA’KILUNE
  8,23,WE LEW ‘ALIMEL-LAHU FIHIM HAJRÆN LE’ESME’AHUM WE LEW ‘ESME’AHUM LETEWELLEW WE HUM MU’RIDUNE
  8,24,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ESTEXHIBU LILLAHI WE LILRRESULI ‘IDHA DA’AKUM LIMA JUHJIKUM WE A’LEMU ‘ENNEL-LAHE JEHULU BEJNEL-MER’I WE KALBIHI WE ‘ENNEHU ‘ILEJHI TUHSHERUNE
  8,25,WE ETTEKU FITNETEN LA TUSIBENNEL-LEDHINE DHELEMU MINKUM HASSETEN WE A’LEMU ‘ENNEL-LAHE SHEDIDUL-’IKABI
  8,26,WE EDHKURU ‘IDH ‘ENTUM KALILUN MUSTED’AFUNE FIL-’ERDI TEHAFUNE ‘EN JETEHATTEFEKUMU EN-NASU FE’AWAKUM WE ‘EJJEDEKUM BINESRIHI WE REZEKAKUM MINET-TEJJIBATI LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  8,27,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TEHUNU ELLAHE WE ER-RESULE WE TEHUNU ‘EMANATIKUM WE ‘ENTUM TA’LEMUNE
  8,28,WE A’LEMU ‘ENNEMA ‘EMWALUKUM WE ‘EWLADUKUM FITNETUN WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE ‘INDEHU ‘EXHRUN ‘ADHIMUN
  8,29,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IN TETTEKU ELLAHE JEXH’AL LEKUM FURKANÆN WE JUKEFFIR ‘ANKUM SEJJI’ATIKUM WE JEGFIR LEKUM WEL-LAHU DHUL-FEDLIL-’ADHIMI
  8,30,WE ‘IDH JEMKURU BIKEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LIJUTHBITUKE ‘EW JEKTULUKE ‘EW JUHRIXHUKE WE JEMKURUNE WE JEMKURU ELLAHU WEL-LAHU HAJRUL-MAKIRINE
  8,31,WE ‘IDHA TUTLA ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATUNA KALU KAD SEMI’NA LEW NESHA’U LEKULNA MITHLE HADHA ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA ‘ESATIRUL-’EWWELINE
  8,32,WE ‘IDH KALUL-LEHUMME ‘IN KANE HADHA HUWEL-HEKKA MIN ‘INDIKE FE’EMTIR ‘ALEJNA HIXHARETEN MINE ES-SEMA’I ‘EW E’TINA BI’ADHABIN ‘ELIMIN
  8,33,WE MA KANEL-LAHU LIJU’ADHDHIBEHUM WE ‘ENTE FIHIM WE MA KANEL-LAHU MU’ADHDHIBEHUM WE HUM JESTEGFIRUNE
  8,34,WE MA LEHUM ‘ELLA JU’ADHDHIBEHUMU ELLAHU WE HUM JESUDDUNE ‘ANIL-MESXHIDIL-HERAMI WE MA KANU ‘EWLIJA’EHU ‘IN ‘EWLIJA’UUHU ‘ILLAL-MUTTEKUNE WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  8,35,WE MA KANE SELATUHUM ‘INDEL-BEJTI ‘ILLA MUKA’EN WE TESDIJETEN FEDHUKUL-’ADHABE BIMA KUNTUM TEKFURUNE
  8,36,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU JUNFIKUNE ‘EMWALEHUM LIJESUDDU ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI FESEJUNFIKUNEHA THUMME TEKUNU ‘ALEJHIM HESRETEN THUMME JUGLEBUNE WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ILA XHEHENNEME JUHSHERUNE
  8,37,LIJEMIZEL-LAHUL-HABITHE MINET-TEJJIBI WE JEXH’ALEL-HABITHE BA’DEHU ‘ALA BA’DIN FEJERKUMEHU XHEMI’ÆN FEJEXH’ALEHU FI XHEHENNEME ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-HASIRUNE
  8,38,KUL LILLEDHINE KEFERU ‘IN JENTEHU JUGFER LEHUM MA KAD SELEFE WE ‘IN JA’UDU FEKAD MEDET SUNNETUL-’EWWELINE
  8,39,WE KATILUHUM HETTA LA TEKUNE FITNETUN WE JEKUNE ED-DINU KULLUHU LILLAHI FE’INI ENTEHEW FE’INNALL-LLAHE BIMA JA’MELUNE BESIRUN
  8,40,WE ‘IN TEWELLEW FA’LEMU ‘ENNEL-LAHE MEWLAKUM NI’MEL-MEWLA WE NI’ME EN-NESIRU